          <span class="text-gradient-pink">Fluid & Physics</span>
          <span class="text-text-primary"> Simulation</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed">
          Real-time fluid dynamics with SPH and grid-based methods. Coupled multi-physics for realistic 
          interactions between fluids, solids, and electromagnetic fields.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
